organization.description: The Humanitarian Data Project (HDP) exists to make humanitarian and crisismapping-related datasets available to groups collecting and managing crisis data. Through datahub, HDP will be launching an open website, which will act as a one-stop shop in guiding individuals as to where humanitarian datasets exist.
organization.title: Humanitarian Data Project
organization.name: hdp
